creator: Scott Wainstock
descriptionHtml:
Find public places to play pinball! Pinball Map is kept up to date by users and lists over 20,000 pinball machines.

This application is a mobile version of the website http://pinballmap.com.
descriptionShort: Find pinball machines to play! Pinball Map is a user-updated pinball locator.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
What is new?

- New Settings page where you can manually choose either dark or light mode
- Redesigned dark mode
- Show commas on long number while entering high scores
- Disabled OTA updates (accidentally sent one out last week, sorry)
- Misc fixes

Also, good job quarantining! Map edits are down to just a handful a day. Stay healthy and safe.

title: Pinball Map

creator: Scott Wainstock
descriptionHtml:

This application is a mobile version of the website http://pinballmap.com.

-Display a Message of the Day on the map screen.
-Updated the FAQ
-Added Resources page
-Lots of bug fixes

descriptionHtml:
Find public places to play pinball! Founded in 2008, Pinball Map is an open source, crowdsourced worldwide map of public pinball machines. It lists over 44,000 pinball machines at over 10,000 locations.

This application is a mobile version of the website https://pinballmap.com.

Features:
- Filter locations by machine, location type, operator, or number of machines
- Save you favorite locations
- See recent nearby map activity
- Add and remove machines to keep the map up to date
- Comment on a machine's condition
- Add your high score for a machine
- View upcoming events
- Submit new locations

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
- Added a Setting to display a Stern Insider Connected icon next to machines that have it enabled on the location details screen.
- Design tweak to location details screen: added a "show more" button for long location descriptions.
- Fixed a bug.
